<i>♪ Say more and more that I am your love ♪</i>

473
00:32:35,078 --> 00:32:37,538
<i>♪ It's all I ask ♪</i>

474
00:32:37,622 --> 00:32:42,251
<i>♪ Our love is already my treasure</i> ♪

475
