<i>♪ And show that everything that we have ♪</i>

478
00:32:55,682 --> 00:33:00,269
<i>♪ Is everything in your heart ♪</i>

479
00:33:01,354 --> 00:33:03,314
<i>♪ Give me a kiss ♪</i>

