<i>♪ And show that everything that we have</i> ♪

482
00:33:13,658 --> 00:33:19,539
<i>♪ Is everything in your heart</i> ♪

483
00:33:19,622 --> 00:33:21,332
<i>♪ Give me a kiss ♪</i>

484
00:33:27,755 --> 00:33:31,384
Selena! Selena! Selena…

485
00:33:37,598 --> 00:33:39,183
<i>♪ Give me a kiss</i> ♪

486
00:33:40,518 --> 00:33:43,896
<i>♪ Show your love with a kiss</i> ♪

487
00:33:45,231 --> 00:33:48,443
<i>♪ And show that everything that we have</i> ♪

488
00:33:49,694 --> 00:33:54,032
<i>♪ Is everything in your heart ♪</i>

489
00:33:55,116 --> 00:33:57,618
- You ever miss that?
<i>- </i>What?

490
00:33:57,702 --> 00:33:59,203
Just being a teenager,

491
00:33:59,287 --> 00:34:01,789
running around on a Saturday night
instead of working?

492
00:34:01,873 --> 00:34:03,207
It doesn't feel like work.

493
00:34:03,291 --> 00:34:04,459
No?

494
00:34:05,835 --> 00:34:08,796
I guess when that's all you've done,
it must feel normal.

495
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,715
- That's her!
- Selena, hi!

496
00:34:10,798 --> 00:34:12,467
Selena!

497
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:13,676
I mean…

498
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:17,013
sometimes, I guess, it'd be fun
to just go out with other kids, but…

499
00:34:17,805 --> 00:34:19,849
during the week, nobody goes out and…

500
00:34:20,349 --> 00:34:22,602
on the weekends,
we have shows, which is fine.

501
00:34:24,312 --> 00:34:26,314
Well, I just want you to be happy.

502
00:34:26,397 --> 00:34:27,857
I am.

503
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:29,108
I am!

504
00:34:34,113 --> 00:34:38,910
<i>…new single "Dame Un Beso"
by a local band called Selena y Los Dinos.</i>

505
00:34:50,797 --> 00:34:51,798
Dad.

506
00:34:53,257 --> 00:34:55,657
I just heard "Dame Un Beso."
